.NET Framework 3.5.name: OVRGazePointer

fields.name: lastHideRequestTime
fields.summary: Last time pointer was requested to be hidden. Usually mouse pointer activity.

fields.name: lastShowRequestTime
fields.summary: Last time code requested the pointer be shown. Usually when pointer passes over interactive elements.

fields.name: positionSetsThisFrame
fields.summary: How many times position has been set this frame. Used to detect when there are no position sets in a frame.

methods.name: RequestShow()
methods.summary: Request the pointer be shown. Hide requests take priority

methods.name: SetPosition(Vector3 pos)
methods.summary: SetPosition overload without normal. Just makes cursor face user

methods.name: SetPosition(Vector3 pos, Vector3 normal)
methods.syntax: public void SetPosition(Vector3 pos, Vector3 normal)
methods.linkedSyntax: public void SetPosition(Vector3 pos, Vector3 normal)

methods.name: Update()

properties.name: visibilityStrength
properties.summary: Used to determine alpha level of gaze cursor. Could also be used to determine cursor size, for example, as the cursor fades out.
